ont-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/5-1683861405453.jpg\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"8\" data-index=\"8\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440908466585669.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440908466585669&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440908466585669.jpg\" alt=\"BRC20 真的懂 Web3？探寻宗教式社区建设，Yuga Labs「猿」宇宙的案例解析\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">图片来源：Bitpush News</em></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">正如创始人 Wylie Aronow (Gordon Goner）所说：「人们用猿创造的任何东西只会让品牌成长」。确实，无聊猿无疑是目前唯一把这套独有的营销模式玩通，还玩得很大的赢家。而在他成功崛起的背后，植根于人们对其品牌文化的喜爱和社区认可，这种高度的共识和价值观认同才是关键。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">持有无聊猿，你就是大佬</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">就像劳力士、就像法拉利，BAYC 在 Web3 界已经发展成为一种地位的象征。是否拥有或是否有能力拥有 BAYC 似乎已经成了行业内鉴定财力的一种标准。随着无聊猿二级市场价格的水涨船高，现在如果你的 Twitter 头像是一张无聊猿的 NFT，那么你的自豪感不亚于开着迈巴赫在街上了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">BAYC 的高速发展离不开社区的作用，自发行以来，在短时间内迅速成长成了一个庞大的社区。对于持有 BAYC 的玩家来说，这不仅是收藏品，更是一个俱乐部。BAYC 成了加密爱好者的潮流代表，他们相信这一领域，并看到该技术在艺术、音乐、游戏和娱乐等行业的许多应用。这种信仰使得人们愿意加入一个拥有相同价值观的社区。而同时又满足了用户心中的归属感。BAYC 的故事背景源于许多 NFT 收藏家的心声：在加密市场中投资者在 NFT 而实现了财富自由的梦。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">同时，他们也把 BAYC 的理念共识从线上拉到线下，从 Web3 推向传统。Yuga Labs 举办了多场线下活动，只有无聊猿的持有者才能够参加，这无疑是一场彰显身份地位的派对，也是一个加密精英圈子，众多大佬都是这个俱乐部里的成员，让无聊猿的价值得到了极大的提升。Yuga Labs 相继举办了互动寻宝活动、线下 Ape FEST、BAYC x MAYC 手游大赛等等。</p><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/5-1683861432419.jpg\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"9\" data-index=\"9\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440908467093573.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440908467093573&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440908467093573.jpg\" alt=\"BRC20 真的懂 Web3？探寻宗教式社区建设，Yuga Labs「猿」宇宙的案例解析\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Ape FEST 、无聊猿派对，图片来源：NFT Evening</em></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当然，支撑起 BAYC 关注度持续不减的关键在于明星的加盟，如歌手贾斯汀比伯、网球名将塞雷娜·威廉姆斯、前 NBA 球员奥尼尔等，有了一众名人加持，这让 BAYC 这名字从未淡出过人们视野中的同时，更进一步地突破了用户圈层。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">写在最后</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">总的来说，不论是共识大会上还是笔者本次的案例分析，Yuga Labs 的核心是给人一个「共富」的愿景并且不断用「赋能」与「分享」来实现，从他们的历史故事到商业模式再到共识建立，从 BAYC、 BAKC 和 MAYC 的 NF，到代币 $APE，再到元宇宙 Otherside，都是再不停增强其 IP 能量。核心是给用户一个足够吸引人的故事，让用户用自己的脑袋思考这个故事该走向何方，在途中又该为其作出些什么贡献。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他们创造的这种新玩法，不仅可以成为加密界的引路人，更可为传统商业提供启示，比起通常依赖于产品或服务的销售， Yuga Labs 的商模式则更注重创造和维护 IP，以及与社区的互动和合作。这种基于社区的协作和共创，是传统商业能够借鉴的，并引发他们思考如何在知识产权分散、共创生态的背景下，发掘新的商业价值。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而 Yuga Labs 的成功，离不开以太坊这块强大的基石。作为一个先进的生态系统，以太坊 NFT 社区在铸造、交易、存储和展示 NFT 方面拥有更成熟和高效的工具和解决方案，为 Yuga Labs 的每一步提供更多的灵感。同时，以太坊生态中有众多活跃的开发者社区，为整个生态系统的发展作出了重要贡献。相比之下，BRC20 还处于起步阶段，但站在巨人的肩膀上才能看得更远，目前正是循着以太坊的脚步在其生态中发现更多的机会和发展空间的大好机会。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在万马齐行的赛道上，Yuga Labs 能否独领风骚，成为杀出重围的黑马？而 BRC20 又能否奋起直追，在这场角逐中站稳脚跟？让我们且行且期待。</p><p><br/></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Y');
INSERT INTO `cms_article_detail` VALUES (440908578209861, 440515705974853, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Blur 近日联合Paradigm 推出Blend 这一P2P <span class=\"wpcom_tag_link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/archives/tag/nft\" title=\"NFT\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">NFT</a></span> <span class=\"wpcom_tag_link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/archives/tag/%e5%80%9f%e8%b4%b7\" title=\"借贷\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">借贷</a></span>协议，以及基于此实现的贷款买NFT 的功能。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Blend 的核心特点有哪些？产品优势是什么？又是如何做到的？本文将带你深入浅出的了解Blend 这一下一代NFT 借贷协议。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Blend 核心特点有：</p><ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 2em; list-style-position: outside; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>点对点，永续借贷，无到期时间，无需预言机</p></li><li><p>贷出方自定可贷金额和APY发布offer，借款方选择offer</p></li><li><p>贷款方退出，借款方需要在30h内还款或者借新还旧，否则清算</p></li><li><p>借款方可随时还款</p></li><li><p>支持先买后付，即首付+贷款买NFT</p></li></ol><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023050409543972928515.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"0\" data-index=\"0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440908758016069.png?type=resource&amp;id=440908758016069&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440908758016069.png\" alt=\"深度解析 Blur 新借贷协议 Blend\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">产品优势</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Blend 核心优势为统一非必要要素，减少系统复杂度，实现借贷关系在系统内部灵活迁移，通过市场博弈来定价风险和收益，最大化满足用户需求。是的，某种意义上来说，Blend 颇有秦始皇“<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">车同轨</em>，<em style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">书同文</em>” 的风采。</p><ol style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 2em; list-style-position: outside; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>相比X2Y2 这些传统点对点模式，Blend 将借款三要素抵押率、利率、期限中期限这一要素统一为永续灵活模式，大大改善了贷款方的流动性问题</p></li><li><p>Blend 将贷款方退出和清算进行统一，毕竟清算本质上就是没有人愿意接盘该项目</p></li><li><p>预言机是服务清算时机决策的， Blend 将退出选择权统一交给贷款方灵活处理。</p></li></ol><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023050409553107039053.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"1\" data-index=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440908758691909.png?type=resource&amp;id=440908758691909&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440908758691909.png\" alt=\"深度解析 Blur 新借贷协议 Blend\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Blend 表面上固定条款（抵押率和利率），实际上由于极具灵活性的退出机制，使得生效中的条款会基本跟随市场平均水平。因为若条款显着差于市场水平，借款方有动力还款然后借其他offer的，若条款显着好于市场水平，贷款方会有动力退出然后发布新offer把钱借给别人。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对于借款方而言，抵押率越高越好，利率越低越好，期限越灵活越好。对于前两点，一方面如上文所述生效条款会跟随市场水平，另一方面Blend 通过对贷款方分配激励点数来操作，设置的可贷金额越高利率越低则点数越多。对于第三点，Blend使用永续+随时还款的设置，实现了借款方期限完全灵活。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023050409555838638818.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"2\" data-index=\"2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440908759236677.png?type=resource&amp;id=440908759236677&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440908759236677.png\" alt=\"深度解析 Blur 新借贷协议 Blend\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对于贷款方而言，抵押率和利率同样跟随市场水平和Blur 激励，没什么吃亏风险。期限也非常灵活，想退出就退出，相当于一方面有着点对点模式的自定义优势，又享受了接近点对池模式的流动性优势，还可以自行制定风控标准灵活退出。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">贷款买NFT</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">贷款买NFT 就跟贷款买房差不多，相当于在买NFT 的同时发起抵押借款，这样就可以交了首付后就拿到房子，即所谓提升资本效率。虽然这和闪电贷ETH → 抵押NFT借ETH部分还款没什么不同，但是首发即整合该功能，有助于给Blend 带来大量新用户助其成长，另外这也体现了Blur 整合统一生态可能实现1+1&gt;2 的效果。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023050409562335189428.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"3\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440908759871557.png?type=resource&amp;id=440908759871557&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440908759871557.png\" alt=\"深度解析 Blur 新借贷协议 Blend\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">其他</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">另外在Paradigm 的设计文档中，贷款方退出时将发起荷兰拍，就是说利率从0%随时间逐步提升至1000%，中间新贷款方随时可以offer，如果到1000%还没人接就清算借款方，把抵押的NFT 给当前贷款方。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023050409564846937479.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"4\" data-index=\"4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440908760498245.png?type=resource&amp;id=440908760498245&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440908760498245.png\" alt=\"深度解析 Blur 新借贷协议 Blend\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但是在Blur 的页面上我们可以看出需要借款方还款或者借新还旧，其实不难推测，是因为目前有借款金额和利率两个变量，而Paragidm 的设计中只考虑了利率一个变量。实际上两者差别不大，都是争取过渡到对借款方最有利的新条款上，不过一个不需要借款方操作一个需要而已。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023050409571938788278.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"5\" data-index=\"5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440908760940613.png?type=resource&amp;id=440908760940613&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440908760940613.png\" alt=\"深度解析 Blur 新借贷协议 Blend\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">不过值得注意的是，Blend 目前也尚未对$Blur 进行太多赋能，$Blur 有设定各项参数的治理权以及半年后打开费用开关的权力，但是一切仍有较大的不确定性。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/2023050409575034889218.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"6\" data-index=\"6\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440908761567301.png?type=resource&amp;id=440908761567301&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440908761567301.png\" alt=\"深度解析 Blur 新借贷协议 Blend\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">总结</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Blend 在传统点对点借贷模式的模式上统一非必要要素，实现“车同轨，书同文”式的效率提升，并与Blur 交易模块进行充分整合，在产品层面上有着较大提升，在代币赋能上较为普通。</p><p><br/></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Y');
INSERT INTO `cms_article_detail` VALUES (440908961955909, 440515705974853, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">原标题：一份全面清单：Web3行业高薪酬的13种工作</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这可能会让许多人感到震惊，但除了成为开发人员之外，Web3还有其他高薪工作。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Web3可能是现代就业市场中跨学科最多的领域</span>，换句话说，它由许多个在不同领域中具有不同程度专业知识的人组成。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这是因为<span class=\"wpcom_tag_link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/archives/tag/%e5%8c%ba%e5%9d%97%e9%93%be\" title=\"区块链\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">区块链</a></span>涵盖了多个研究领域，包括密码学、应用数学、经济学、资本市场等等。而且，Crypto项目也需要非技术性的岗位来推动项目的实施。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这些非技术岗位包括市场营销、社区管理、人力资源、作家等。要使Web3成为一个运行良好的整体，需要很多种工作。</p><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/4d717a4d2d2ad0fbe0997d495c03dcc9.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"0\" data-index=\"0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909189541957.png?type=resource&amp;id=440909189541957&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909189541957.png\" alt=\"高薪酬的Web3行业：13个工作的全面清单\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">然而，并不是所有的岗位都有着同样的需求。因此，某些职位提供了更多的薪酬和有竞争力的福利。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你想通过除了持有数字资产之外的其他方式增加你的收入，那么就看看目前Web3行业最高薪酬的13种工作吧。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">人力资源</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">人力资源是组织内负责管理和协调员工各方面事务的部门。<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">人力资源部门主要负责招聘、雇佣、培训、员工福利、绩效评估、薪酬和员工关系</span>。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">其主要目标是确保组织拥有合适的人才，并确保他们得到有效管理，以便为公司整体做出贡献。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">文案编辑员</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">文案编辑员是为不同的营销和广告材料撰写书面内容（也称为文案）的人。其主要目标是创造有说服力和吸引力的信息，以便成功地推广商品和服务、传达所需的信息，并说服目标受众采取特定行动。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此外，文案编辑员的职责还可能包括编辑和校对内容，确保内容的一致性和符合品牌调性、进行市场调研、了解目标受众、与营销团队合作、开发创意概念，以及撰写标题、标语和正文。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">销售</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">销售是向客户销售产品或服务以产生收入并达到业务目标的过程。<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">销售是公司内部的一项重要职能，因为它直接和公司的盈利挂钩</span>。</p><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/c4e546eae60f283e83d7cf5d143580cb.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"1\" data-index=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909191098437.png?type=resource&amp;id=440909191098437&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909191098437.png\" alt=\"高薪酬的Web3行业：13个工作的全面清单\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">基本上，销售团队的目标是产生收入并实现组织设定的销售目标或指标。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">有效的销售实践包括了解客户需求、建立关系以及提供卓越的体验，以提高客户满意度和忠诚度。<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">一些销售岗位提供无限/无上限的佣金，使其成为收入最高的Web3工作之一</span>。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">智能合约开发者</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">智能合约开发者专门从事智能合约的设计、开发和实施，他们的职责包括智能合约工程、测试和调试以及安全审计。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此外，他们将项目从最初的概念和设计阶段带到生产阶段，与工程领导者以及产品团队密切合作，制定可行的、明确的路线图。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而且，因为精通区块链架构和编程，<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">所以这些智能合约开发者即使是在入门级职位上也能获得丰厚的报酬</span>。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">社交媒体经理</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在通过各种社交媒体平台提升Crypto行业内的品牌知名度方面，社交媒体经理发挥着至关重要的作用。他们的主要职责是针对机构和零售客户实施有影响力的社交媒体策略。</p><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/c33127ad35ba3cf274aff1215f7f21e2.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"2\" data-index=\"2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909192208453.png?type=resource&amp;id=440909192208453&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909192208453.png\" alt=\"高薪酬的Web3行业：13个工作的全面清单\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此外，他们还参与执行旨在实现更高转化率的营销计划。他们还可能承担额外的任务，比如分析竞争对手、分析市场趋势或制作高质量的社交媒体内容。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">技术作家</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">就Web3工作而言，写作是一个广泛的类别，但技术作家和一般的写作职位不大相同。技术作家专门从事创建清晰、简洁和用户友好的文档，以及与技术主题相关的内容（例如白皮书或文档）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">因此，技术作家在弥合复杂技术信息与非技术用户或受众之间的差距方面发挥着至关重要的作用</span>。简而言之，他们能够理解复杂的技术概念，并将其转化为易于理解和使用的材料。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">前端开发者</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">前端开发者专门负责构建去中心化应用程序（DApp）、基于区块链的Web应用程序用户界面 （UI）和用户体验（UX）组件。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此外，前端开发者还将区块链技术集成到用户界面中，使用户能够与去中心化网络和智能合约进行交互。有时，这涉及连接到区块链节点，从区块链中检索数据，并以用户友好的方式显示数据。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">法律合规</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Web3和区块链公司必须遵循监管环境，确保符合适用的法律法规</span>。这包括了解并遵守金融法规、数据保护和隐私法、反洗钱法规、证券法以及其他与所在司法管辖区相关的特定法律要求。</p><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/b8f5726ec9105a4d21a3d6e3cbc019b5.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"3\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909192626245.png?type=resource&amp;id=440909192626245&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909192626245.png\" alt=\"高薪酬的Web3行业：13个工作的全面清单\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此外，Web3和区块链公司还必须解决与其技术相关的知识产权问题，例如专利、许可、商标和版权。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">电路工程师</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">电路工程师专门从事零知识电路的设计和实现，他们的主要职责是设计和构建能够实现高效可靠的零知识证明的电路。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">这涉及对密码学基元、数学概念和计算复杂性的深入理解</span>。此外，工程师还与研究人员、密码学家和软件开发人员合作，将理论协议转化为实际可操作的解决方案。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">高管</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最高管理层是组织中担任高级领导职位的管理人员，他们负责指导和监督公司的战略方向和运营。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">他们通常直接向公司董事会或股东进行汇报，并在决策、制定目标和推动公司整体正常运行方面发挥关键作用。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">每位高管通常都有特定的职责和专业知识领域，专注于公司运营的不同方面</span>，例如：首席执行官（CEO）、首席财务官（CFO）、首席技术官（CTO）等。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">项目经理</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">项目经理负责规划、组织和监督组织内项目的成功执行。他们在管理资源、时间表、预算和利益相关者以实现项目目标方面发挥关键作用。</p><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bcb111704fe41d5592a3a6e35150e9a5.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"4\" data-index=\"4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909193474117.png?type=resource&amp;id=440909193474117&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909193474117.png\" alt=\"高薪酬的Web3行业：13个工作的全面清单\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">项目经理制定全面的计划，概述任务、时间表、资源分配等。他们还通过定义项目范围和目标、寻找和分析风险以及更新团队和利益相关者来提高内部工作流程的生产力。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">元宇宙内的各种角色</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">元宇宙是一个集体虚拟共享环境，用户可以在其中与其他用户和虚拟对象实时交互。在虚拟现实（VR）、增强现实（AR）等沉浸式技术不断地发展下，这一概念最近引起了很多关注。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在元宇宙中，各个行业都有许多潜在工作机会，这些工作包括社区经理、平面设计师或者编程员。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"wpcom_tag_link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/archives/tag/dao\" title=\"DAO\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">DAO</a></span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">DAO，即去中心化自治组织，是一种通过区块链网络上的智能合约来运作的组织。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">它被设计为自治的，也就是说，<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">它的运作是由预先编程的规则来管理的，决策是通过其成员或通证持有者的共识来做出的</span>。</p><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/8c791267a92c6362ba345952bac2c0ab.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"5\" data-index=\"5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-hover);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909194166341.png?type=resource&amp;id=440909194166341&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909194166341.png\" alt=\"高薪酬的Web3行业：13个工作的全面清单\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">由于DAO运行在区块链网络上，并且经常涉及去中心化金融（DeFi）和Crypto项目，所以工作机会主要围绕这些领域展开。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在Web3领域，不仅有很多职业道路，而且还有很多高薪工作。<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">你越往上爬，就越能得到更有竞争力的交易</span>。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">换句话说，高薪只是开始。除了赚更多的钱，从事Web3工作通常还会带来奖金、更多的带薪休假时间、远程工作等。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果你是Web3新手，可以考虑一下以上所说的这些高薪酬的Web3工作是否适合你。</p><p><br/></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Y');
INSERT INTO `cms_article_detail` VALUES (440909325451333, 440515705974853, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">撰写｜Stacy Muur</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">编译｜深潮 TechFlow</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"wpcom_tag_link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/archives/tag/l2\" title=\"L2\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">L2</a></span> 战争正在升温，以太坊扩展的未来预计将围绕 L3、SuperChain 和 Hyperchain 发展。如何跟上这一波趋势？让我们一起深入了解 L2 发展的前沿领域。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023062916474999772419.jpg\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"0\" data-index=\"0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909511819333.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440909511819333&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909511819333.jpg\" alt=\"以太坊扩展解决方案的演变：OP Stack、Arbitrum Orbit、Polygon 2.0...\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">为什么会演变为这样的格局？虽然以太坊作为 L1 运行，但它必须具备与互联网相同规模的操作能力。然而，目前没有任何单个 L2 拥有这种能力。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023062916475043799406.jpg\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"1\" data-index=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909514408005.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440909514408005&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909514408005.jpg\" alt=\"以太坊扩展解决方案的演变：OP Stack、Arbitrum Orbit、Polygon 2.0...\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">从更高维度来看，Web3 开发者目前有三个选择：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">• 在以太坊上部署，但会牺牲可扩展性。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">• 选择 L2 解决方案，但会面临对特定生态系统的依赖风险。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">• 部署并维护自己的链，但可能导致流动性碎片化。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此外，实现互操作性也是一个重大挑战。事实证明，我们使用跨链桥应对这一挑战的努力是脆弱的，并且一直受到恶意行为者的攻击。新的挑战需要创新的解决方案。新的挑战需要创新的解决方案。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下一波 Rollup，如 Optimism 上的 OP Chains、Arbitrum Orbit 上的 L3 或 zkSync 上的超级链，将赋予不同目标的各个实体创建自己定制环境的能力。你可以将其看作是部署新的 Rollup 链=创建一个新的网页。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">让我们更详细地了解核心扩展参与者提供的解决方案。</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Optimism &amp; OP Stack</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在 2022 年 10 月，Optimism 提出了：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">•&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">OP Stack（OP 堆栈）</span>——一个用于创建可扩展和互操作的各种类型<span class=\"wpcom_tag_link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/archives/tag/%e5%8c%ba%e5%9d%97%e9%93%be\" title=\"区块链\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">区块链</a></span>的模块化开源蓝图。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">•&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Superchain（超级链）</span>—— 紧密集成和统一的建立在 OP Stack 之上的 L2。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">简单来说，OP Stack 可以被看作是一个“建立 L2”的超市。它提供了不同的层次（模块），可以轻松定制以满足项目的特定需求。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">通过利用这种方法，他们可以释放超级链未来的潜力。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023062916475837610500.jpg\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"2\" data-index=\"2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909515391045.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440909515391045&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909515391045.jpg\" alt=\"以太坊扩展解决方案的演变：OP Stack、Arbitrum Orbit、Polygon 2.0...\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在 6 月初，Optimism 宣布将他们的 L2 Rollup 迁移到 Bedrock。这个发布代表了 OP 堆栈的首次正式上线，使 OP 主网成为代币交换最具成本效益的以太坊 L2 Rollup。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023062916475914669482.jpg\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"3\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909516075077.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440909516075077&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909516075077.jpg\" alt=\"以太坊扩展解决方案的演变：OP Stack、Arbitrum Orbit、Polygon 2.0...\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此外，Bedrock 还有以下优势：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">• 将存款时间从 10 分钟缩短至 3 分钟。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">• 通过支持故障证明和 ZK 证明来增强证明模块化。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">• 允许在单个 Rollup“块”内执行多个交易。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在完成 Bedrock 升级后，Optimism 的下一步是过渡到超级链。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">超级链是一个由 L2（OP 链）组成的去中心化网络，将共享安全性、通信层和开源技术堆栈（OP 堆栈）。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023062916475826558489.jpg\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"4\" data-index=\"4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909516755013.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440909516755013&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909516755013.jpg\" alt=\"以太坊扩展解决方案的演变：OP Stack、Arbitrum Orbit、Polygon 2.0...\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">接下来是什么？Alpha 部分从这里开始。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">• Optimism 的 L2 Rollup 链 ——超级链的第一个成员。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">• Coinbase 即将推出的 Base L2 ——第二个成员，预计今年宣布上线主网。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">• Worldcoin 也承诺在 OP Stack 上构建。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">• AEVOXYZ，一个去中心化期权交易所，最近与 Conduit 合作推出了基于 OP Stack 的 Rollup。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">• BNB Chain 上的 opBNB 也利用了 OP Stack。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">• 由 OurZORA 开发的 Zora Network 是基于 OP Stack 构建的 L2 解决方案。</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Arbitrum Orbit</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Arbitrum 目前是按照 TVL（总锁定价值）计算的最大和最具优势的 L2 网络，总价值超过 59 亿美元，占据了超过 60%的市场份额。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Arbitrum 提供 4 个核心产品：</p><ol start=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 2em; list-style-position: outside; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Arbitrum One</span>：这是 Arbitrum 生态系统的第一个主网 Rollup。</p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Arbitrum Nova</span>：一种 AnyTrust 解决方案，专为成本敏感和高交易量预期的项目设计。</p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Arbitrum Nitro</span>：这个技术软件堆栈驱动 Arbitrum L2，使 Rollup 更快、更便宜，并且更加兼容以太坊虚拟机（EVM）。</p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Arbitrum Orbit</span>：这个开发框架允许在 Arbitrum 主网上创建和部署 L3。</p></li></ol><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">L3 Rollup，也被称为应用链，对于结算交易到 Arbitrum 链起着至关重要的作用。它们是 Arbitrum 扩展旅程的下一个阶段的基础，并且是实现他们愿景的解决方案。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023062916480337521891.jpg\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"5\" data-index=\"5\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909517463621.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440909517463621&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909517463621.jpg\" alt=\"以太坊扩展解决方案的演变：OP Stack、Arbitrum Orbit、Polygon 2.0...\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Arbitrum 非常注重可定制性。Orbit 旨在与即将推出的 Arbitrum Stylus 升级兼容。这种兼容性为开发人员使用 C、C++ 和 Rust 构建 dApp 提供了可能性，并扩展了 Arbitrum 的多功能性和覆盖范围。</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">zkSync &amp; Hyperchain</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">现在，让我们转向 zkSync 及其对以太坊扩展的未来愿景。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Hyperchains 是 zkSync 对 L3 的设想，被构思为一个广阔的无信任且可定制链接的区块链生态系统。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023062916482340985023.jpg\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"6\" data-index=\"6\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909518164037.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440909518164037&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909518164037.jpg\" alt=\"以太坊扩展解决方案的演变：OP Stack、Arbitrum Orbit、Polygon 2.0...\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">简单来说，Hyperchain 指的是以太坊上的独立 ZK 链。这些链通过一系列可定制且完全无信任的超级跨链桥网络相互连接。这种方法有助于克服通常与非本地桥梁相关的漏洞。</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">StarkWare &amp; Fractal Scaling</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">从理论上讲，该系统可以拥有无限数量的 Hyperchain 来代表整体。这就是 StarkWare 作为 Fractal Scaling 先驱者需要做的。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023062916481422138101.jpg\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"7\" data-index=\"7\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909518938181.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440909518938181&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909518938181.jpg\" alt=\"以太坊扩展解决方案的演变：OP Stack、Arbitrum Orbit、Polygon 2.0...\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">总之，StarkWare 的多层网络论文提出 L2 设计用于通用扩展，而 L3 应用于定制扩展。然而，除了最初发布的这篇论文之外，StarkWare 没有作出任何进一步的公告。</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Polygon 2.0</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Polygon 在 6 月初发布了关于他们 L2 发展的下一个阶段的最新公告。Polygon 2.0 旨在创建“互联网的价值层”。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">该解决方案旨在通过一系列升级提高 Polygon zkEVM、PoS 和超网之间的互操作性。通过将零知识技术与现有的 PoS 机制相结合，Polygon 旨在增强安全性和隐私保护。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在 Polygon 2.0 中，他们的目标是结合两种技术的优势。Polygon 团队最近的一项公告揭示了他们计划在 2024 年第一季度结束时将 Polygon PoS 转换为 zkEVM validium 的计划。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">总的来说，以太坊扩容解决方案的演变是未来几个月值得密切关注的话题，每一个 L2 巨头都给出了自己的方案，但最终鹿死谁手，还犹未可知。</p><p><br/></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Y');
INSERT INTO `cms_article_detail` VALUES (440909610135621, 440515705974853, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">撰文｜veDAO</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">加密空投是 web3 项目分发代币并为其平台造势的一种流行方法，特别是初创公司最常使用。加密空投也是最受用户欢迎的营销策略之一，通过认真的研究与聪明的参与，用户可以通过空投第一时间接触认识最新最优质的项目，同时也可以获得不错的经济收益。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在这篇文章中，veDAO 将深入分析下加密空投，包括它的定义、历史、流程与分类等，同时提供安全参与撸空投的经验与注意事项。最后 veDAO 给大家推荐近期 6 个最值得参与的空投机会。</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一、空投定义</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">空投（Airdrop）是指在区块链领域中，通过向特定的数字钱包地址发送免费的加密代币的一种行为。也就是说空投就是项目方赠送加密资产给用户的一种行为。对于项目方来说，加密空投是一种营销策略，旨在推广新项目和它的加密代币，提高对项目的认识，并促进采用。对于用户来说，加密空投代币是免费发送的，但有时可能会被要求完成特定任务，通过参与加密空投可以获得不错的经济收益。加密空投不仅限于新的加密项目，成熟的 web3 项目也可以使用该策略来完善代币的分配和奖励忠诚的社区成员。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023061913400005426398.jpg\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"0\" data-index=\"0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909759356997.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440909759356997&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909759356997.jpg\" alt=\"深入加密空投：历史、流程与分类，以及近期 6 个最值得参与的机会 \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">二、空投历史</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">空投（airdrop）是币圈行之有年的文化。最早的加密货币空投发生在 2010 年 6 月，曾与中本聪（Satoshi Nakamoto）共同开发比特币系统的软件工程师 Gavin Andresen 架设了一个名为&nbsp;Free Bitcoins 的网站。用户只要在网站中贴上自己的比特币收款地址，就能获赠 5 颗比特币。当年价值仅 1 美分（约 0.3 元台币）。加密空投真正成为项目方重要的运作手段，一般认为是从 2014 年开始的。想要了解加密空投的本质，就必须对它的演变历史有一个清晰的认识。</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 2em; list-style-position: outside; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>2014 年：第一个加密空投由一个名为「Auroracoin」的项目发起。它向冰岛所有公民分发免费代币，作为促进采用新加密代币的一种策略。不过最后该项目和代币都以失败告终。这时的空投没有任何交互及其他要求，确认是社区成员就行。</p></li><li><p>2017 年：随着 ICO 热潮，空投越来越受欢迎，大量 web3 新项目开始使用空投作为吸引潜在投资者和用户的一种方式。Electroneum 是这个时期成功使用空投策略的项目之一，它向用户免费空投 5000 多个代币，非常成功，在活动的前两周就有超过 120000 名用户下载了该应用程序并创建了帐户。</p></li><li><p>2018-2019 年：加密空投开始变得更加复杂和有针对性，项目使用它们来奖励早期采用者、社区成员和忠诚用户。Steemit 是出色地通过空投建成了强大社区的大项目之一，它根据用户在平台上的参与程度向用户分发名为「Steem」的代币。</p></li><li><p>2020 年：defi 的兴起带来了一种新型的空投形式，也就是 web3 项目像流动性提供者或参与流动性挖矿活动的用户分发代币。著名 Dex 项目 Uniswap 在 2020 年 9 月的 UNI 空投。这是加密历史上规模最大、知名度最高的空投之一， 并催生了无数的模仿者。</p></li><li><p>2020 年加密空投也开始被用作一种以公平和透明的分配代币的方式，通过「快照」空投等机制，根据用户之前的交互或其他参与程度奖励用户。DeFi 项目 1INCH 是最早尝试使用快照空投公平分配代币的项目之一。</p></li><li><p>2021 年：围绕空投的监管政策开始变得更加清晰，一些司法管辖区要求将空投注册为证券发行。</p></li><li><p>2022 年：选择空投的项目越来越多。BAYC 对其 NFT 持有者的 Apecoin 空投、 Optimism 项目 OP 代币的空投以及 Apto 对其早期采用者的空投都是这一年有影响力的空投活动。2022 年开始对空投的要求越来越高，开始有查女巫做筛选，空投开始多维度，获得空投需要多重要求。</p></li><li><p>2023 年：当前，空投已是加密市场最重要组成部分之一，今年以来，空投的项目和次数都经历了巨大的增长。Arbitrum 空投，第一个小时就领取了超过 4200 万的 ARB，是今年最轰动的空投。</p></li><li><p>总结：加密空投一直在不断的迭代进化，其已成为加密市场的重要组成部分。按参与空投的难以程度，历史上空投可以分为以下几个阶段：确认是社区成员、简单登记或 0 转、简单交互阳光普照型、查女巫做筛选和重度参与用户，多维度作为空投条件。</p></li></ul><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">三、空投流程</h1><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2023061913400041675959.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"1\" data-index=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440909759909957.png?type=resource&amp;id=440909759909957&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440909759909957.png\" alt=\"深入加密空投：历史、流程与分类，以及近期 6 个最值得参与的机会 \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">空投作为营销工具，每个具体的项目都会根据自己的特定需求选择不同的加密空投类型，每种空投类型的工作模式也是不同的。 一般性的空投过程可分为：</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 2em; list-style-position: outside; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>项目背后的团队决定空投给用户的代币数量。下一步是选择他们将用来分发代币的目标人群和平台，同时为用户获得空投代币设置资格要求。</p></li><li><p>用户从正在进行的空投项目中筛选一个优质的自己感兴趣的 web3 项目。</p></li><li><p>一般空投都需要用户满足的特定要求，才有资格获得免费代币。这些要求可能包括在社交媒体上关注项目、分享帖子、加入 discord/Telegram 群组、填写调查问卷以及与项目交互任务等。 有些项目要求用户完成 (KYC) 验证才能参与，而有些项目只需要用户注册即可。加密空投的要求因项目的喜好而异，主要目的还是项目或新代币获得尽可能多的宣传和采用。</p></li><li><p>满足要求后，用户提交的详细信息以注册空投。</p></li><li><p>注册完成后，用户需要等待分发代币。</p></li><li><p>项目一般通过智能合约执行空投，代币自动分配到用户钱包。</p></li><li><p>分发代币后，用户将在钱包中收到它们。收到代币后，用户可以选择是继续持有代币或者在加密交易所进行交易。</p></li></ul><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">四、空投类型</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">每种空投类型都有独特的特征和目的，我们需要了解不同类型的加密空投。以下是流行的加密货币空投类型。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">持有者空投</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">持有者空投向钱包中持有一定数量数字货币的人免费发放代币。项目团队通常会在特定日期和时间，对用户的加密货币持有量进行快照拍摄。如钱包余额达到最低要求，接收人将根据快照时的持有量免费领取代币。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">许多新项目向比特币 (BTC)、以太币 (ETH) 或其他已获得成功的代币的钱包持有者空投代币，因为他们拥有该领域规模最大的社区。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">标准空投</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最原始的空投方式，用户只需注册相关钱包或合约即可获得免费空投。不需要其他信息。空投快速简便，但项目开发人员对每个用户获得的代币数量设置了限制。他们遵循先到先得的原则。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">赏金空投</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">赏金空投一般是事前公告获得空投的要求，需要用户参与促销活动。赏金空投需用户完成某些任务，例如在 Twitter 分享该项目的相关发帖、加入该项目的官方 Telegram，或在 Instagram 上创建帖子并标记若干朋友。要领取赏金空投，用户需填写包含钱包地址信息的表格，并提供完成任务的证明。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">独家空投</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">独家空投仅限向指定钱包发送加密货币。一般而言，空投代币接收人曾经接触过该项目，要么是活跃社区成员，要么是项目的早期支持者。这些空投通常被用作奖励忠实用户和围绕项目建立强大社区的一种方式。2020 年 9 月，去中心化交易平台 (DEX) Uniswap 向所有在特定日期之前与平台协议交互过的钱包空投了 400 UNI。持有治理代币的用户将有权对未来与项目发展相关的决策进行投票。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">水龙头空投</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">水龙头空投就是定期（通常是每天或每周）向参与者分发少量代币。这些空投通常价值很小，旨在鼓励用户定期与项目互动。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">硬分叉空投</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这个有点不同。当硬币从其原始区块链硬分叉时，会创建一个新代币，而持有原始代币的人将在钱包中收到等量的新代币。最著名的例子是 2017 年发生的比特币现金（BCH）硬分叉：持有 BTC 的比特币用户自动收到等量的 BCH。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">总结</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">加密货币空投，依据公告领取资格的时机可简单分为两大类：事前公告和事后追认型。赏金空投和水龙头空投多为事前公告型，其他类型空投多为事后追认型，也可以是事前公告型。项目方会根据他们的动机和获客规划来选择要执行的加密货币空投类型。</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">五、经验与注意事项</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当参与加密货币空投活动时，以下几点是 veDAO 总结梳理的一些空投的经验和注意事项，用户在参与空投活动时可作为参考：</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 2em; list-style-position: outside; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">做研究：</span>在选择参与空投活动之前，对选择的项目和它的团队做充分的研究。</p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">不要将空投视为投资：</span>建议将空投视为红利而非主要的投资策略。</p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">使用单独的电子邮件地址和钱包地址：</span>它可以帮助用户保护用户的个人信息不被共享。</p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">密切关注项目：</span>空投通常有时间限制，用户需要在规定的时间内完成任务或提交钱包地址。如果错过了时间，就无法获得代币。保持项目最新动态和信息的更新也可以帮助用户规避所有可能的骗局。</p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">请耐心等待：</span>空投分发可能需要时间，并且可能由于各种因素而延迟。</p></li><li><p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">谨防诈骗：</span>空投诈骗事件屡见不鲜，用户切勿参与不靠谱项目的空投活动，切勿泄露您的私钥或个人信息。myEtherWallet 网络钓鱼骗局是最近发生影响很大的骗局，诈骗者创建了一个假网站并推广了一个假空投，要求用户输入他们的私钥才能接收代币。</p></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">专门空投工具：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://airdrops.io/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">http://airdrops.io</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://dropsearn.com/airdrops/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">http://dropsearn.com/airdrops/</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://defillama.com/airdrops\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">http://defillama.com/airdrops</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://99airdrops.com/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">http://99airdrops.com</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://alphadrops.net/alpha\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">http://alphadrops.net/alpha</a></p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">六、推荐撸空机会</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">经过大量筛选和研究，下面 veDAO 帮大家梳理下值得参与的近期 6 个可能空投或即将空投的潜力项目。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">LayerZero</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">LayerZero (ZRO) 是一种全链互操作性协议。能够通过可配置的免信任提供真实且有保证的消息传递。它目前在大多数主要区块链上运行，包括 Ethereum、Avalanche、Polygon、BNB Chain、Aptos、Fantom、Arbitrum 和 Optimism。LayerZero 尚未推出其代币，但该团队在其文档中提到了 ZRO 代币。但是，预期项目会将代币空投给他们的 dApp 用户。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">以下是参与任何潜在空投的一些建议：</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 2em; list-style-position: outside; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>在 Stargate Finance 上质押 STG 和投票</p></li><li><p>使用 Stargate、USDC、Aptos 和 LiquidSwap 桥</p></li><li><p>使用 SushiSwap 跨链互换</p></li><li><p>使用比特币桥</p></li><li><p>与 LayerZero 上的其他 dApp 交互</p></li><li><p>在 Stargate Guild 中获得角色</p></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">需要注意的是 LayerZero 团队没有关于空投的官方公告。所以任何建议的参与方式都只是猜测。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">zkSync</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">zkSync 是一个 ZK Rollup，在以太坊区块链上提供可扩展和低成本的交易。这是通过将有效性证明连同捆绑的交易一起提交给以太坊智能合约， zkSync Era Mainnet Alpha 现已向公众开放。该团队表示，他们将在未来推出原生代币，这让人们希望届时可以空投一些代币。据推测，要获得 zkSync 空投资格，用户应该：</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 2em; list-style-position: outside; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>在 MetaMask 上添加 zkSync Era Alpha 主网</p></li><li><p>与 zkSync Lite 和 zkSync Era Mainnet Alpha 交互</p></li><li><p>在 zkSync 的 Crew3 上完成任务</p></li><li><p>与 zkSync 生态系统互动，例如 Orbiter Finance 或 ZigZag。</p></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">值得注意是因为一些 zkSync dApps 可能还没有启动他们的代币。这样您就有机会获得双倍空投。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">StarkNet</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">StarkNet 是在以太坊之上运行的去中心化 Validity-Rollup（「ZK-Rollup」），在不牺牲安全性或兼容性的情况下为去中心化应用程序提供无限的计算能力。它利用安全且可扩展的密码证明系统 STARK 来确保交易安全可靠。StarkNet 是免许可的，这意味着任何人都可以使用它而无需第三方批准。StarkNet 的 alpha v0.11.0 刚刚在 Testnet 上线，预计不久之后将进行主网升级。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">获得潜在 StarkNet 的 STRK 代币空投的最佳方式是与他们的测试网互动。此外，StarkNet 上有一些协议还没有代币。因此，使用他们的 DApps 也可以让你获得他们的空投，让你获得双倍奖励。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Polygon zkEVM</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Polygon zkEVM (MATIC) 是以太坊的第 2 层扩展解决方案，它利用零知识证明的扩展能力，同时保持以太坊兼容性。Polygon 的联合创始人 Sandeep Nailwal 在推特上强烈暗示，将为 zkEVM 用户提供巨大的 MATIC 空投。获得潜在空投的最佳方式是与 Polygon zkEVM 主网进行交互。为此，将 Polygon zkEVM 添加到 MetaMask。然后，通过本地网桥或第三方网桥（例如 Orbiter Finance）连接到 Polygon zkEVM。最后，与 QuickSwap 交互，这是目前唯一部署在 Polygon zkEVM 上的活跃 dApp。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Vela Exchange 空投</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Vela Exchange 是一个去中心化永续合约平台，旨在利用链下订单簿和链上结算的混合模式，提高 DeFi 衍生品的交易速度和安全性。根据官方文档，Vela 用户可以根据合成资产的表现建仓，杠杆率高达 100 倍。Vela 将于 2023 年 6 月 26 日进行空投和主网启动。项目官方 Twitter 上已暗示用户最大化交易量就是获得最大空投的关键。此外，参加他们的闪电交易大赛不仅可以让你有机会赢得他们的奖品，还可以为你提供更多的空投代币。第一场比赛以 10,000 美元 USDC 和 2000 美元 eVELA 奖励的奖池结束。Vela 将举办第二场快闪比赛，比赛将进行调整以支持各种规模的交易者。然而，主要活动将是他们的 Grand Beta 交易大赛，Vela 承诺将提供大奖。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Blur NFT Marketplace</h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Blur (BLUR) 的第 1 季空投于 2023 年 2 月 14 日结束。Blur 宣布他们将在第 2 季空投超过 3 亿美元的 BLUR，该计划原定于 2023 年 4 月举行，但目前已推迟。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">要参加 Blur 的空投第 2 季，用户可以将他们的钱包连接到 Blur 的平台并竞标 NFP。Blur 已确认在第二季度将分发超过 3 亿美元的代币。空投是在基于点的系统上进行的。该系统根据 24 小时的交易量奖励 NFT 收藏的出价。参与者还可以通过忠诚度赚取更多积分来最大化他们的 BLUR 代币空投。对于第 2 季，Blur 还推出了 Blend（Blur Lending 的缩写）。Blend 是一种针对 NFT 的点对点永久借贷协议，它允许 NFT 持有者以其 NFT 为抵押借入 ETH，而无需出售它们。随着 Blend 的推出，Blur 团队还引入了借贷积分，某些 NFT 收藏品的借贷积分翻倍。Blur 延期造成积分贬值，已导致社区普遍不满，随着代币价格的下跌，参与二季交互的利润可能达不到预期效果。</p><p><br/></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Y');
INSERT INTO `cms_article_detail` VALUES (440909824315461, 440515705974853, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">随着 Web3 行业的发展，用户和项目方数量都在不断快速增长，竞争也越来越激烈。如何在竞争中胜出，选对工具是关键，正所谓工欲善其事必先利其器，智者当借力而行。无论用户和项目方学会利用好 Web3 任务型平台工具，都将事半功倍。</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一、web3 任务平台简介</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">web3 任务类平台主要业务是提供关注项目方社交账号、答题、链上操作以及任务悬赏等任务，用户完成后可获得积分、NFT 以及 token 奖励。Web3 任务平台起到了 Web3 入门教育，以及链接用户与项目方的作用。Web3 任务类平台起始于 2020 年 Web 2 的社交媒体营销服务商 Gleam.io 开始为 web3 行业提供服务，其后 web3 任务型平台也大量涌现，Web3 任务型工具经过两三年的发展，已经出现了上百个项目，并且正在成为加密世界的新流量中心。</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">二、用户如何利用 web3 任务平台</h1><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 2em; list-style-position: outside; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>web3 任务平台一般用户体验做的相对较好，有的平台做的还比较有趣，操作也相对更简单容易，所以对于 web3 新人可以做为链上操作入门，学习 web3 行业基础知识和了解学习项目或社区。</p></li><li><p>对于资深 web3 从业者，通过 Web3 任务管理平台，可以在同一平台上接触并了解到多类项目和社区，有些平台还有项目或社区的分类和筛选功能，用户可以省去很多时间和精力，寻找到自己感兴趣的优质项目。</p></li><li><p>对于撸空投挣收益的用户，通过做 web3 任务平台上的任务可以获得相应奖励，如 NFT、POAP、空投资格、代币奖励等，投入的成本以及风险相对较低，是一个功能高级的空投聚合类网站。</p></li><li><p>此外用户通过在 web3 任务平台上做任务可以积累自身的链上和链下的活动证明，有利于建设个人的 Web3 身份，打造个人 web3 声誉。</p></li></ul><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">三、项目方如何利用 web3 任务平台</h1><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 2em; list-style-position: outside; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>项目方可以通过发布任务并给予奖励的形式，吸引平台上的用户参与以达到宣传目的。对于发展初期且粉丝量不高的新项目而言，借助于 Web3 任务管理平台的流量效应，可以实现相对更好的营销效果。对于成熟项目方可以多做激活和留存类活动，也可以做拉新活动。</p></li><li><p>项目在 web3 平台上发布任务相对更简单及时有效，项目方可以快速完成一个效果显著的 Web3 运营活动，为自己的项目和产品增加用户量与使用量。</p></li><li><p>很多 Web3 任务平台有用户的链上链下数据分析功能，项目方可根据任务平台的数据筛选出真实用户并发放奖励，做到防止空投给无效用户和以及预防女巫攻击，做到精准投放精准营销。</p></li><li><p>利用 Web3 任务平台项目方可以与其平台上他项目或社区发起多项目的联合市场活动。</p></li><li><p>Web3 任务平台都漂亮的、多维度、精细化的数据仪表盘展示面板，项目方可以了解自己本次活动的效果好坏（转化率）、触达的用户画像是否精准（活跃度）、活动任务设置是否合理（每个任务的完成率）等等。可以动态调整运营策略。</p></li></ul><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">四、六大 web3 任务平台</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当前 Web3 任务平台工具可谓是百花齐放。从共同点来说，它们都是任务型营销工具，都是 web3 用户增长工具。但各平台的切入点和侧重点还是有一定的差别的，按照平台的切入点可分为流量类、教育类以及细分垂直类三类。根据业务模式侧重点的不同，平台可以分为偏向 to C、to B、to C+to B 三种。VeDAO 从赛道中选取了 6 个代表项目给大家做个简单介绍。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">4.1、Galxe</span></h3><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910072909893.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440910072909893&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" alt=\"智者当借力而行：浅析六大 Web3 任务平台 \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Galxe，原名 Project Galaxy，是目前最大的 Web3 任务平台。截至 2023 年 6 月 24 日，已与超过 2700&nbsp;个项目方 / 社区合作，推出超过 10000&nbsp;个任务，拥有超过 1100 万 Galxe ID 的用户。Galxe 允许项目方在平台上发行 NFT，满足条件的用户可获得 Mint 资格，项目方还可以通过 平台的数据凭证提供定制化服务。用户可以在平台上看到各个项目发布的任务，并能够从中寻找潜在空投、参与社区活动、发现新项目。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Galxe 搭建了一套自己的数字身份凭证 Galxe ID，以及从链上标记 OAT。其通过对链上数据的分析，给不同用户打上了各种标签，对于每个 Quest，也将产生一个 Credential 集合，作为白名单导出到第三方进行应用（如 Token 派发）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Galxe 推出的任务多为特定项目任务，主要为关注项目方推特，转推，加入 Discord，链上交互等。用户完成任务获得的奖励主要为 OAT（链上成就 NFT）和其他 NFT，其中部分 NFT 可以售卖。任务多且较为繁琐，不适合 Web3 入门教育，但适合空投猎人和进阶选手积累链上交互记录。平台的商业模式偏向 to B，属于流量类平台。</p><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910074142789.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440910074142789&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" alt=\"智者当借力而行：浅析六大 Web3 任务平台 \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Galxe 也有实人认证模块：Galxe Passport，用户提供 KYC 信息后可铸造一个 SBT，这也是 Galxe 在防女巫方面的措施。Galxe Credentials 是用户交互凭证，通过读取用户链上链下交互记录，自动授予给用户。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">4.2、Zealy（原 Crew3）</span></h3><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910074835013.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440910074835013&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" alt=\"智者当借力而行：浅析六大 Web3 任务平台 \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Zealy 是一个侧重于对社区进行宣传的平台，主要目标是帮助 web3 社区不断成长。Zealy 以 Web3 Discord 作为其发展定位，并具备较高的社交属性。社区内活动模板较多，包括日常打卡、内容创作、邀请任务等运营任务。相对于其他平台，Zealy 更聚焦且分类十分清晰，该平台还具备积分排名系统。在 Zealy 中，部分项目任务需要写文、截图证明、邀请等方式才能完成，以过滤很多自动化羊毛党，保证用户真实性。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">平台提供的任务基本都是特定项目任务，用户通过关注项目方推特，转推，加入 Discord，注册项目账号，项目知识答题等任务。任务多为项目方营销获客设计，因此项目的商业模式也是偏 to B 的, 也属于流量类平台。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">4.3、QuestN</span></h3><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910075961413.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440910075961413&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" alt=\"智者当借力而行：浅析六大 Web3 任务平台 \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">QuestN( 原 Quest3) 是一个由 Hogwarts Labs 孵化的 Web3 任务活动平台，是 GRT14 捐赠项目之一。平台是一个以服务长尾 B 端用户为特色的 Web3 任务凭证平台。在大部分主流任务凭证平台，如 RabbitHole，Galxe，只有具有一定规模的 B 端客户才能通过平台的筛选发布任务，而 QuestN 不设置门槛，小 B 端客户如 KOL，社区，DAO 等都可以发布任务，但平台为了保证 B 端客户的质量，也要求绑定官网，社交账号等，对于提供 token 奖励的任务，还要求 B 端客户提前将奖励 token 存入金库，起到验资的作用。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">QuestN 上提供的任务基本都是特定项目任务，用户通过关注项目方推特，转推，加入 Discord，注册项目账号等任务，提供的奖励有 token，NFT，白名单等。任务多为项目方营销获客设计商业模式也是偏 to B 模式的， 也属于流量类平台。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">4.4、Layer3</span></h3><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910076813381.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440910076813381&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" alt=\"智者当借力而行：浅析六大 Web3 任务平台 \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Layer3 设计了一套“New to Web3”系列任务，由浅入深地引导用户完成 Layer2，DAO，DeFi，NFT 等领域的链上交互，完成后可获得 NFT 和经验值奖励。完成任务获得的 NFT 也可出售，但普遍价格不高。同时，也提供了特定项目任务，主要操作为链上交易，质押，添加流动性等，但不同于 Galxe，这些任务难度较低一些，且大多没有最低交易额要求，进行价值 1U 的交互也可完成任务，并且也提供了任务指导，因此，对不想花费太多资金的 Web3 初学者比较友好。项目方主要是为了获得客户，也会与各类交互平台合作。项目方需要向平台方支付一定费用，并向用户提供一定激励，可能是空投也可能是其他激励，所以平台的商业模式是 to B+to C 结合模式。可归于教育类项目。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">4.5、RabbitHole</span></h3><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910077698117.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440910077698117&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" alt=\"智者当借力而行：浅析六大 Web3 任务平台 \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">RabbitHole 是一家老牌的去中心化的链上激励交互平台。当前产品分为 web3 新用户教育平台 Skill 和广告投放 Quest 两类。一类是 Skills，目前有四种 Skills，分别是 Layer2，DAO，DeFi，NFT。需要完成的任务多为基本的 Web3 链上操作。其中每个任务的 Details 中都提供了详细的教程。完成这些任务后，用户将获得一个不可转让的“Intro to L2” NFT。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">另一类任务是 Quests，这些多为单个项目方发布的交互任务，除了奖励 NFT，有的 Quest 还会奖励项目代币，但奖励项目代币的任务通常需要 BrightID 实人认证防女巫（女巫攻击即为一个用户伪装成多个身份进行操作）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">总体而言，RabbitHole 提供了较为详细的 Web3 链上操作入门教育，适合小白用户使用，合作项目方较弱。RabbitHole 曾在 2022 年 2 月份宣布完成 1800 万美元 A 轮融资，由 Greylock 和 TCG Crypto 领投。商业模型偏 to C, 可归为教育类项目。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">4.6、TaskOn</span></h3><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910078328901.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=440910078328901&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" alt=\"智者当借力而行：浅析六大 Web3 任务平台 \" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">TaskOn 是一个 Web3 任务协作平台，致力于 Web3 项目的营销和运营增长。TaskOn 是 Moonbeam 系列应用的一部分。平台能够提供一些自动化功能，减少操作流程。例如，API-Verified 可以帮助自动验证参与者是否进行产品特定操作。该平台还具备自动发奖功能，可以在活动结束后代替活动方立刻发奖，而活动方所有的操作只有创建活动，将足够的奖励（Token 或 NFT）充进自己的 TaskOn 账户；TaskOn 还可以替活动主办方创建活动，进一步减少主办方的操作。在当前的 Web3 任务平台中，TaskOn 是功能精简易用，发展速度较快的平台之一。该平台因具备一系列防机器人措施，是目前真实用户率最高的平台之一（高达 92.9%）。平台商业模式偏 to B, 属于流量类平台。</p><p><br/></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Y');
INSERT INTO `cms_article_detail` VALUES (440910133866565, 440515705974853, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Web3是构架在<span class=\"wpcom_tag_link\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><a href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/archives/tag/%e5%8c%ba%e5%9d%97%e9%93%be\" title=\"区块链\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">区块链</a></span>上的价值网络，上面的一切价值皆可被代币化，代币是价值的数字化形式，并在 Web 3 的价值网络中自由、高效地组合、流转和分配。HashKey Group 的肖风博士提出的“三代币模型”，非常清晰地解释了价值的各个维度，即功能型代币（Utility Token）、权益型代币（Security Token）和非同质化代币（NFT）分别代表着使用权、所有权和数字通证。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">而 SAFT（Simple Agreements for Future Tokens）作为 Web3 投融资中最常见的协议，是通过 Token 的形式来捕获 Web3 项目的价值。本文将结合 HashKey Group 白皮书《Web3 新经济和代币化》以及美国 Cooley 律所 SAFT 白皮书，从三代币模型的角度来理解 SAFT，Web3 代币投融资以及 Token 投融资的价值捕获方式。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/eXfVPLhYna.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"0\" data-index=\"0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910320660549.png?type=resource&amp;id=440910320660549&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440910320660549.png\" alt=\"从三代币模型理解 SAFT 以及 Web3 代币投融资\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">(from: How to Invest in Web3: The Next Phase of the Internet)</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">TL; DR</span></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Web3 新经济是利益相关者经济，核心是使用权制度；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">三代币模型中的功能性代币、权益性代币、NFT 分别代表着使用权、所有权和数字通证；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">使用权不能被股份化，但是可以被代币化，即功能性代币，是使用权的一种价值表示，获取的是网络效益的价值；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">SAFT 本身是一份投资协议，SAFT 只适用于功能性代币，通过两步走的协议机制，实现了 Token 从证券型代币到功能型代币的转变，从而一定程度规避美国 SEC 的证券监管；</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Web3 项目投融资，目的都是去捕获项目的价值，股权和代币投资的区别在于确定价值于何处实现，通过何种方式去捕获。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">一、Web3 新经济的三代币模型</span></h3><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/8B6t2761Wd.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"1\" data-index=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910321303621.png?type=resource&amp;id=440910321303621&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440910321303621.png\" alt=\"从三代币模型理解 SAFT 以及 Web3 代币投融资\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, monospace, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: pre-wrap; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.45; background-color: rgb(43, 48, 59); border-radius: 3px; border: 0px; color: rgb(238, 238, 238); overflow-x: scroll;\">(from:&nbsp;解析代币化，引领新经济！&nbsp;《Web3新经济和代币化》白皮书在2023香港Web3嘉年华发布)</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">深入理解三代币模型的本质，对于理解 Web3 投融资中不同形式的价值捕获非常有帮助。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">无论是在 Web1 还是 Web2 的经济模型中（监控资本主义），都是由平台享有最终信息数据的所有权，平台通过变现后产生了巨大的商业价值，催生了如 Facebook、Googel 等平台级的商业巨头，但这与一般的用户参与者无关。<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">而基于区块链网络的 Web3，则是基于一套价值网络的经济模型（利益相关者资本主义），强调数据可信、数据主权和价值互联。在一切价值都可代币化的前提下，价值不仅仅包括了所有权，更重要的价值是使用权。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">所有权具有独占性，难以分割。所有权制度下的组织形态（一般为公司），其目标是股东利益最大化，是股东资本主义的体现。使用权则是非独占的，具有多重共享性，可以多次授权、许可，甚至做到开源、CC0 的无限循环。使用权制度的核心是利益相关者资本主义，原有的组织形态就不一定合适，以开源组织、非营利组织为基础的去中心化自治组织（DAO）就天然地适合利益相关者资本主义，成了 Web3 的新经济模式的最主要组织形式。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">在使用权制度下，组织中所有参与者以利益相关者的身份进行大规模协作，做出自身的贡献，共享组织价值</span>。在这样的背景下，项目股东所代表的股东所有权已经没有意义，真正有价值的是项目的使用权。<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">使用权不能被股份化，但是可以被代币化。</span>结合区块链分布式账本技术，使用权能够以 Token 的形式标准化和份额化，这与每一个在项目网络中的参与者的利益都有关系，即功能性代币（Utility Token）。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"https://cdn-img.panewslab.com/panews/images/M76OZp5i1K.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"2\" data-index=\"2\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910322221125.png?type=resource&amp;id=440910322221125&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440910322221125.png\" alt=\"从三代币模型理解 SAFT 以及 Web3 代币投融资\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, monospace, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: pre-wrap; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.45; background-color: rgb(43, 48, 59); border-radius: 3px; border: 0px; color: rgb(238, 238, 238); overflow-x: scroll;\">(from:&nbsp;Web3&nbsp;新经济和代币化)</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">在 Web3 经济模型、使用权制度、利益相关者资本主义的基础上，围绕项目构建的三代币模型——功能型代币（Utility Token）、权益型代币（Security Token）和非同质化代币（NFT），将根据自身的价值形态，与所有参与的利益相关者共享价值。</span>例如，利益相关者只有拥有该区块链网络、系统或应用的 Token，才具有使用该网络、系统或应用的权利；又或者代币可以是表决权的凭证，可以参与社区投票、表决和治理等，这些都是使用权的体现。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">l功能型代币（Utility Token）捕获的是该 Web3 网络、系统或应用的网络规模效应。生态应用和用户的体量越大，市场对该代币的需求就越高，代币的价格依靠市场的价值发现。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">l权益型代币（Security Token）捕获的是股权、债权等权益类资产未来现金流的价值。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">lNFT 则是事物底层资产的数字化资产形式，可以称为“数字通证”。NFT 与其锚定的底层资产价值相关，价值来源多种多样。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">二、SAFT 的法律属性</span></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">SAFT（Simple Agreements for Future Tokens）——未来代币投资协议，是专门针对架构在区块链网络上 Web3 项目的一种投资协议。SAFT 约定由项目方以未来网络上线后代币的认购权作为对价，来换取投资者当下的资金，用于项目网络当下的开发建设。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">由于权益型代币（Security Token）是各个司法辖区的重点监管对象，SAFT 通过建立一套协议机制，最终实现功能型代币（Utility Token）网络上线的效果，来规避美国证监会及相关法律对于 Web3 项目代币投融资行为的监管。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/TG16ZNH6g9.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"3\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910339829829.png?type=resource&amp;id=440910339829829&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440910339829829.png\" alt=\"从三代币模型理解 SAFT 以及 Web3 代币投融资\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, monospace, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: pre-wrap; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.45; background-color: rgb(43, 48, 59); border-radius: 3px; border: 0px; color: rgb(238, 238, 238); overflow-x: scroll;\">(from:&nbsp;https://saft-project.org/)</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">由美国 Cooly 律所主要操刀的 SAFT 白皮书（The SAFT Project: Toward a Compliant Token SaleFramework）于 2017 年 10 月 2 号发布，首次提出了 SAFT 的交易模式，旨在为 Web3 项目提供了一条基于美国证券法体系下的合规 Token 发行路径，主要分为两个步骤：</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/NojdYSHN4i.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"4\" data-index=\"4\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910340227141.png?type=resource&amp;id=440910340227141&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440910340227141.png\" alt=\"从三代币模型理解 SAFT 以及 Web3 代币投融资\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（1）项目开发阶段：对于尚在开发阶段的 Web3 项目，投资人通过金钱的投入之后，其利润的预期依赖于项目方开发团队对网络的管理和开发。由于代币并没有实际效用，这个阶段的代币性质，更加类似于股权的一种价值表示，捕获的价值是 Web3 项目的未来现金流的能力。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这种投资行为可能满足 Howey Test 的标准，属于“投资合同”（Investment Contract），从而要被纳入美国证监会严格的证券监管。但可以根据美国证券法 Regulation D Rule 506 申请豁免，而无需进行证券登记，将投资人仅限于合格投资人（Accredited Investors）。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"https://cdn-img.panewslab.com/panews/images/FY54H2VBlU.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"5\" data-index=\"5\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910340661317.png?type=resource&amp;id=440910340661317&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440910340661317.png\" alt=\"从三代币模型理解 SAFT 以及 Web3 代币投融资\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（2）项目开发完成上线阶段：对于已经开发完成并上线项目网络，其发行的代币（Already-functional Utility Token）具备允许用户访问该 Web3 项目生态网络的诸多效能（使用、消费、治理等）。这个阶段的代币性质，是使用权的一种价值表示，被定义为功能型代币（Utility Token）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">由于该代币已经具有了实用属性，一般而言投资人购买代币的主要目的是获取项目网络的实用价值，不是为了单纯的获利。而且，对于一个去中心化的代币经济体系或治理体系，该代币在二级市场的价格完全受到市场的供需关系影响，而不由项目开发团队的贡献主导。这大大区别于（1）项目开发阶段代币的作用。因此 SAFT 白皮书认为，这样的 Utility Token 不具备“证券”的属性，一般不会纳入美国证监会的严格监管。但SAFT 的目的是去合美国 SEC 的规，严格来说只适用于专业投资者（Accredited Investment），并不适合大部分中小投资人。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/8Quw2Lz71E.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"6\" data-index=\"6\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910356332613.png?type=resource&amp;id=440910356332613&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440910356332613.png\" alt=\"从三代币模型理解 SAFT 以及 Web3 代币投融资\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, monospace, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: pre-wrap; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.45; background-color: rgb(43, 48, 59); border-radius: 3px; border: 0px; color: rgb(238, 238, 238); overflow-x: scroll;\">（from:&nbsp;Kraken’s&nbsp;Legal&nbsp;Chief&nbsp;Has&nbsp;No&nbsp;Time&nbsp;to&nbsp;Educate&nbsp;Firms&nbsp;About&nbsp;Crypto）</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">虽然我们看到 SEC 在最近的 Kik 案和 Telegram 案中对于 SAFT 发出了诸多挑战，但是总感觉是功能型代币（Utility Token）的设计以及发行节奏上存在瑕疵。作为 SAFT 白皮书起草者之一，最懂 Crypto 以及美国证券法的律师之一，目前担任 Karken 总法律顾问的 Marco Santori，都在 2023 年 2 月因 Karken 的 Staking as a Service 业务被 SEC 干翻车，更不用说各个项目网络不同、Token 功能设计不同、代币经济设计不同、投资人不同的项目 SAFT 协议了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Web3 投融资在法律上有诸多方式，如涉及股权的 SPA（Share Purchase Agreement）、SAFE（Simple Agreement for Future Equity），以及涉及代币的 TPA（Token Purchase Agreement）、SAFT（Simple Agreement for Future Tokens），或者两者结合的 SAFE + Token Warrant/Side Letter。具体采取哪种形式，需要基于 Web3 投融资的本质。</p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">三、Web3 投融资的本质</span></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Web3 项目投融资，最重要的在于确定价值于何处实现。</span>在为股权类项目估值时，更多关注的是公司的未来现金流的能力，因为股东享有公司利益分配的合法权益。在为代币类项目估值时，传统现金流的估值模式并不适用，更多关注的是项目网络规模效应，网络与代币之间的需求，以及代币的功能。因此，对比代币融资项目，代币经济非常重要。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/OB5pkk6Aa1.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"7\" data-index=\"7\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910356852805.png?type=resource&amp;id=440910356852805&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440910356852805.png\" alt=\"从三代币模型理解 SAFT 以及 Web3 代币投融资\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, monospace, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: pre-wrap; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.45; background-color: rgb(43, 48, 59); border-radius: 3px; border: 0px; color: rgb(238, 238, 238); overflow-x: scroll;\">(from:&nbsp;Connecting&nbsp;Web3&nbsp;Wallet&nbsp;to&nbsp;Twitter&nbsp;Account)</pre><h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（1）Twitter 的 Web3 假想</h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">目前创作者生态的 Web2 互联网巨头 Twitter，是通过公司这一组织形态运行，其目标是股东利益最大化，体现的是股东资本主义，投资的价值在于公司对于未来现金流的获取能力，股票价格反映未来现金流的价值。而试想一个基于 Web3 新经济模型的 Twitter，以其代币激励网络生态上的所有参与者（内容创作者、开发者、验证者、其他市场参与者等），共同维护 Twitter 生态网络并推动治理。代币的效能不仅是交换媒介，还能为用户访问 Twitter 生态网络、消费 Twitter 生态网络上的产品/服务、对 Twitter 生态网络的决策进行治理等提供效能。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">这种 Web3 新经济模型将经济利益和治理权力从中心化实体释放到整个去中心化的生态网络中，参与的所有利益相关者都能够分享到他们所创造的价值，体现的是利益相关者资本主义。这种模式下，Twitter 的股权不一定有意义，Twitter 的代币将取代股权去捕获 Twitter 生态网络上更大的价值，代币价格反映生态网络对于代币的供需关系。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/ANg9s57yvh.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"8\" data-index=\"8\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910357307461.png?type=resource&amp;id=440910357307461&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440910357307461.png\" alt=\"从三代币模型理解 SAFT 以及 Web3 代币投融资\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">(from: https://dune.com/hildobby/NFTs)</p><h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; font-size: 18px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">（2）Opensea 与 Blur</h4><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">曾经全球最大的 NFT 交易平台 Opensea 于 2022 年 1 月获得了 Paradigm 和 Coatue 的 3 亿美元的融资，估值 133 亿美元。Opensea 的现金流以其交易手续费为主要支撑，Opensea 的这类项目可以理解为 Web3 中典型的股权投融资项目，它们在许多方面可以适用传统的商业模式，投资人捕获的是公司未来现金流的价值，股权投资是更可取的。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">同期，2022 年 3 月，Blur 拿到了 Paradigm 的 1100 万美元融资。在 Opensea 这座大山面前，Blur 在一年后直接通过激活社区的方式（给社区参与者代币空投的形式），开启了 NFT 市场的流动性盛宴，实现了对 Opensea 网络效应的弯道超车。Blur 的这类项目可以理解为 Web3 中典型的代币投融资项目，投资人捕获的是 Blur 网络生态规模效应，生态应用和用户的体量越大，市场对该功能型代币的需求就越高，代币的价格依靠市场的价值发现。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">但考虑到 Blur 代币在上市之后的萎靡以及 Token 功能的局限，可以看出<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">如何设计好代币的功能以及代币经济模式是项目长远运行的重中之重</span>。</p><p></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/uzHQws30Xn.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"9\" data-index=\"9\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/19/440910357737541.png?type=resource&amp;id=440910357737541&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://localhost/dev-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/19/440910357737541.png\" alt=\"从三代币模型理解 SAFT 以及 Web3 代币投融资\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p></p><pre class=\"wp-block-preformatted\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: SFMono-Regular, &quot;Liberation Mono&quot;, Consolas, Menlo, monospace, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;; white-space: pre-wrap; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.45; background-color: rgb(43, 48, 59); border-radius: 3px; border: 0px; color: rgb(238, 238, 238); overflow-x: scroll;\">(from:&nbsp;https://docs.blur.foundation/tokenomics)</pre><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">所以可以看出，<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Web3 项目投融资，目的都是去捕获项目的价值，区别在于确定价值于何处实现，通过何种方式去捕获。</span></p><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.46; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 18px; position: relative; padding-left: 18px; border: 0px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">四、写在最后</span></h3><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Web3 项目价值流动性的大幅提升，对于项目方提出了更高的要求，其需要在白皮书融资阶段就能够相对清晰地描述项目未来的模式以及代币经济的安排，否则难以衔接后面的 SAFT 以及发展规划。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">因此，在项目早期模式尚未定型的阶段，也可以采用股权融资 + 代币条款的设置（SAFE + Token Warrant/Side Letter），一方面同样能够解决 SAFT 规避美国证券监管的目的，一方面也能为项目提供股权融资的途径，同时保留代币融资的可能。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">方式可以多种多样，但是Web3项目必须产生价值，否则都是雾里看花。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">——END——</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">本文仅供学习、参考，希望对您有所帮助，不构成任何法律、投资意见，not your lawyer，DYOR。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Reference:</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">[1] HashKey Group, Web3新经济和代币化白皮书</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://www.hashkey.com/cn/insights/web3-new-economy-and-tokenization-whitepaper\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">https://www.hashkey.com/cn/insights/web3-new-economy-and-tokenization-whitepaper</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">[2] Cooly, The SAFT Project: Toward a Compliant Token SaleFramework</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://www.cooley.com/news/insight/2017/2017-10-24-saft-project-whitepaper\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">https://www.cooley.com/news/insight/2017/2017-10-24-saft-project-whitepaper</a></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">[3] 北拓研究 | 股权vs代币：投资模式与价值捕捉</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/TqgqIon3Ijq77yCe1wx5ZA\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/TqgqIon3Ijq77yCe1wx5ZA</a></p><p><br/></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Y');
INSERT INTO `cms_article_detail` VALUES (441444239904837, 440515705974853, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">LDNews 消息，Polygon Ventures 发推称，去中心化身份初创公司 Intuition 正在构建全栈解决方案「Git for knowledge」，将去中心化存储、身份、W3C 可验证证明和 DID 等开放协议原语相结合。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此前报道，6 月 16 日，Intuition 完成 400 万美元种子轮融资，Superscrypt 领投， Shima Capital、Avon Ventures、WW Ventures、Matrixport Ventures、Polygon Ventures 和 ConsenSy 等参投。Intuition 计划于今年晚些时候公开发布其协议和首批应用。Intuition 的协议和中间件允许开发人员轻松地将公司的证明和知识图谱集成到他们自己的应用中。Intuition 最初将与构建在协议之上的知识图浏览器一起启动，并将直接显示有关网络钱包地址的人类可读数据。 <a class=\"kx-more\" href=\"https://twitter.com/PolygonVentures/status/1682073093957906432\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\">[原文链接]</a></p><p><br/></p>', NULL, NULL, '0');
INSERT INTO `cms_article_detail` VALUES (441454841741381, 440515705974853, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">作者｜Huobi Research</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">封面设计｜LDNews DAO</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">导读</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">区块链带来了信任、流动性、透明度、安全性、效率和创新，但加密行业的熊市似乎很难找到新的增长点，加密行业急需一个赛道承载新的叙事。RWA代币化能够打通传统金融和加密金融的通道，承载数十万亿美元的资产市场，对加密行业来说可以是超越牛熊周期的生命之水，所以区块链诞生至今一直在尝试的RWA代币化，但受到了技术、监管、市场等多重因素的阻碍。如今，RWA赛道又被热议，多家机构开始布局。RWA项目已呈现种类繁多、DeFi为主、收益高、风险高的特点，已经逐渐步入大众视野，但项目总体上还存在流动性差、早期阶段、缺少价格发现等问题。RWA赛道是否能在未来几年爆发也要看基础设施的发展和监管体系的完善，这篇研报也提出了代币标准化和合规化是RWA赛道发展的必经之路。尽管RWA赛道面临多重挑战，行业发展始终是向前走的，我们已经看到不少创新项目的出现，尤其是基于美债美股、中小企业融资、实物资产的项目上，这些项目主要特点在于：1. 与传统金融机构合作；2. 最大化项目和代币的收益；3. 引入更多的合法第三方参与。这些特点能够部分解决RWA代币化上出现的问题，包括监管、中心化、链上链下身份、资产估值等，我们期待未来更多的项目丰富RWA赛道。</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1. 正在酝酿的叙事</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">经历了长达1年多的熊市，整个加密市场的市值严重缩水，资金不断流出，链上活动萎靡，DeFi收益已经不再有吸引力，场内互割严重。现在的我们无法想象，加密行业应该靠什么启动下一个牛市。加密市场和传统金融市场还有很大的差距。但我们也可以从熊市发生的一些暴雷事件中，窥见巨大的商机。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">可以说，导致2022年一些大型机构破产的主要原因是利用山寨币进行融资和借贷，当山寨币在熊市出现爆跌，进一步加剧了贷款的清算，死亡螺旋开始。我们看到，是机构和信贷推动了2021年的牛市，也是它们促成了2022年的熊市。实际上，信贷推动了价值数万亿美元的业务和全球经济的大部分发展。它带来的潜力是巨大的，目前，在 DeFi 市场上，越来越多的协议进入股权和债务融资等传统信贷市场。虽然带来了一些风险，但是这是唯一能够将超过 800 万亿美元的传统金融市场引入到链上的方式。<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">弥合加密市场和传统金融之间的巨大差距，我们需要做的是现实世界资产的代币化。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在今年上半年，传统和加密行业开始关注RWA板块。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">首先是高盛宣布旗下数字资产平台 GS DAP 正式上线，而该平台已经帮助欧洲投资银行（EIB）发行 1 亿欧元的两年期数字债券。不久后，管理规模超 1000 亿的私募股权公司 Hamilton Lane 在 Polygon 网络上将其 21 亿美元旗舰股权基金的一部分代币化，向投资者出售；电气工程巨头西门子也在区块链上首次发行 6000 万欧元的数字债券。其次，一些政府机构也开始试水RWA，包括新加坡金融管理局 (MAS)将与摩根大通、星展银行合作。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4月，币安宣布成为Layer1区块链Polymesh节点运营商；其次，MakerDAO、Aave、Maple Finance 等DeFi协议在RWA赛道上动作频繁，更多加密投资公司也在寻求RWA的项目。目前，RWA板块的项目已经超过50个，主要集中在金融资产类，包括固定收益、TradFi，少部分在地产和碳信用领域。近期，RWA概念代币都有所上涨，有些涨幅超过10倍以上。2023年上半年的一波蓄力，是否预示着RWA在未来几年将引领加密叙事？</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2. RWA的前世今生</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">RWA概念在区块链行业并不陌生，最早RWA的项目是“资产上链”的BTM比原链。目前，最成功的RWA就是数字美元USDT、USDC，即把美元映射到链上并代币化。稳定币潜移默化地影响着整个加密行业，现已成为重要基石。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">RWA的全称为现实世界资产的价值代币化（real world assets- tokenization），是将有形或无形资产中的所有权价值（以及任何相关权利）转换为数字代币的过程。这使得资产的数字所有权、转移和存储无需中央中介，价值映射到区块链上并交易。RWA可以是有形或无形资产。</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 2em; list-style-position: outside; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>有形资产包括：房地产、艺术品、贵金属、交通工具、运动俱乐部、赛马等。</p></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">无形资产包括：股票和债券、知识产权、投资基金、合成资产、收入分成协议、现金、应收账款等。</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.1 RWA赛道现状</h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">RWA赛道项目种类繁多，多以DeFi为主，主要有三种类别：1. 基于美债、股票、房地产、艺术品等链下资产的固定收益类项目；2. 基于公开市场发行或交易的公共信贷类项目；3. 基于碳信用等虚拟资产的交易市场类项目。除此之外，还有垂直公链等基础设施项目。</p><ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 2em; list-style-position: outside; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p>固定收益类基于美债和股票市场，为私人和机构提供贷款。这些项目与链上其它DeFi借贷类项目的唯一区别在于抵押品可以是现实世界资产。</p></li><li><p>公共信贷类可以通过跟踪美债或其它债券建立投资基金以供加密用户投资。</p></li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">数据方面，根据RWA.xyz网站统计，包括Centrifuge、Maple、GoldFinch、Credix、Clearpool、TrueFi、Homecoin 在内的8个RWA借贷协议，共计发放贷款额度$4.38b，用户可获得平均APR达到10.52%，主要服务于中等以下的发展水平国家。这些信用借贷协议提供的收益比大部分DeFi借贷高，但在2022年的机构暴雷事件中，Maple Finance发生了6930万美元的债务违约。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1686888852492349.jpg\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"0\" data-index=\"0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"DeFi\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/21/441456002629701.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=441456002629701&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://admin.1000mz.com/prod-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/21/441456002629701.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a>根据Dune数据分析面板，以太坊RWA项目中，$wCFG, $MPL, $GFI, $FACTR, $ONDO, $RIO, $TRADE, $TRU, $BST的持币地址数也在不断增加，目前达到3.9k。</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1686888852491805.jpg\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"1\" data-index=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" alt=\"DeFi\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/21/441456003518533.jpg?type=resource&amp;id=441456003518533&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://admin.1000mz.com/prod-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/21/441456003518533.jpg\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></h1><p><br/></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Y');
INSERT INTO `cms_article_detail` VALUES (441455009255493, 440515705974853, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Radiant Capital&nbsp;是一个跨链 DeFi 借贷协议，通过使用 LayerZero 作为跨链基础设施，来实现全链杠杆借贷和可组合性。目前Radiant作为跨链借贷赛道内早期跑出来的项目，具有一定的具有先发优势。并且后续随着Radiant在V3、V4版本全面集成LayerZero的全链技术，有望为项目带来新的拐点，将其全链借贷进一步推向市场，值得关注。</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">投资概要</span></h1><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当下随着公链和二层赛道的不断发展，生态之间的流动性将不可避免的被进一步分割。头部借贷项目Compound Finance此前推出Gateway提供跨链借贷的测试网；Aave在V3版本中也会支持跨链借贷，近期Aave V3的提案分别通过了V3 Portals将添加Hashflow/Wormhole和Stargate作为“白名单桥”的投票；Uniswap、Sushiswap等主流DEX同时在多条链上部署。诸多老牌DeFi蓝筹的入场，也都表明了不想错过多链市场早期的行业红利。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Radiant Capital是一个跨链 DeFi 借贷协议，团队将自身定位为全链（omnichain）借贷协议，旨在实现不同的链与链之间的杠杆借贷和可组合性，使用户可以在其支持的DeFi协议中获得杠杆，简化用户在不同链与链之间，资产跨链借贷的操作。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Radiant Capital项目的亮点在于</span>：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1）作为LayerZero生态上首个推出的跨链借贷协议，Radiant目前完成了早期项目的冷启动，并且捕获了一定规模的市场份额和用户群体，在该赛道内具有先发优势。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2）Radiant V2版本的改进，延长了项目的生命周期，缓解了$RDNT代币的通胀问题，dLP的设计也有望为协议带来更多的流动性，但其带来的影响是一个长期的过程，仍有待进一步的观察。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3）基于LayerZero的Radiant，在跨链借贷层面，由于共享一个代币标准（OFT），因此能够在所有LayerZero支持的链上实现流动性共享，而无需依靠外部第三方跨链桥额外的信任假设。后续Radiant如果在其V3、V4版本能做好预言机与中继之间的安全假设，实现合约层面的去信任化，那么在资产跨链的安全假设方面，相比目前市面上主流的借助第三方跨链桥实现资产跨链的方式可能将更占优。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">该项目的风险点在于</span>：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1）团队匿名，虽然Radiant在其官方文档和社区里面都有简单介绍过团队情况，但具体成员的履历情况皆未披露。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2）单就借贷领域Radiant并没有什么创新的技术优势，其主要沿用了Aave的设计。随着后续Aave V3推出自己的跨链借贷功能——Portal，那么将对Radiant产生一定的冲击。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3）回顾Radiant的发家史，很大一部分因素离不开协议高额的代币激励，此外还与宏观层面行情的回暖、Arbitrum生态火热、LayerZero全链预期等诸多因素有一定的关联度。这也使得在当下Radiant的预期有点过度被消耗。如果单从FDV / TVL 比率来看，目前（2023年4月25日）Aave为0.29，Compound为0.3，而Radiant约为1.68。这表明Radiant的全流动市值高于其TVL，对比借贷协议Aave和Compound，可以说Radiant目前的市值虚高。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4）Radiant Capital基于LayerZero的底层架构，在预言机方面利用Chainlink来确保预言机报价的准确性，中继（Relay）方面的选择暂时未作披露，仍存在一定安全隐患。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">综合来看，虽然Radiant Capital目前仍面临着一些问题，但凭借LayerZero的全链技术，以及项目目前已有的先发优势，未来仍有机会在跨链借贷领域进一步取得更多的成就，因此<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">值得关注。</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">说明：头等仓最终评定的【关注】/【不关注】，是按照头等仓项目评估框架对项目当前基本面进行综合分析的结果，而非对项目代币未来价格涨跌的预测。影响代币价格的因素众多，项目基本面并非唯一因素，因此，不可因为研报判定为【不关注】，就认为项目价格一定会跌。此外，区块链项目的发展是动态的，被我们判定为【不关注】的项目，若其基本面发生重大的积极变化，我们将有可能会调整为【关注】，同样地，被我们判定为【关注】的项目，若发生重大恶性改变，我们将会警示所有会员，并有可能会调整为【不关注】。</p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">1.基本概况</span></h1><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">1.1项目</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">简介</span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Radiant Capital是一个跨链DeFi借贷协议，团队将自身定位为全链（omnichain）借贷协议，旨在实现不同的链与链之间的杠杆借贷和可组合性。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">1.2基本信息</span></h2><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023071118415497629976.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"0\" data-index=\"0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/21/441455962669125.png?type=resource&amp;id=441455962669125&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://admin.1000mz.com/prod-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/21/441455962669125.png\" alt=\"研报｜跨链DeFi借贷协议Radiant Capital\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p><br/></p><h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-size: 24px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">2.项目详解</span></h1><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">2.1团队</span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Radiant Capital官方文档中披露了16名团队成员，但只有名字和负责的岗位，团队成员履历皆未披露，本质上是一个匿名团队。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此外，Radiant在今年4月份的一篇官方博文中提到，Radiant Capital 拥有一支 14 人的团队，他们之前来自摩根士丹利、苹果和谷歌，团队成员自2020年夏初以来一直从事DeFi行业，并且有许多团队成员自2015年以来就从事加密货币。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">如果一个区块链项目的团队成员匿名，可能存在以下风险：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1）<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">信任问题</span>：团队成员匿名可能会引起投资者和用户的不信任。因为匿名团队无法提供个人身份证明和背景信息，这可能会导致投资者和用户认为项目可能是一个骗局或诈骗项目，从而降低他们对项目的信任度。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2）<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">责任问题</span>：匿名团队成员可能会让团队成员逃避责任，如果项目出现问题，用户和投资者将很难找到相关团队成员来解决问题。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3）<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">缺乏透明度</span>：匿名团队通常不公开其经验、技能和教育背景等信息，这使得投资者和用户无法确定项目可信度和团队的专业水平。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4）<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">营销问题</span>：匿名团队可能会在宣传方面遇到障碍。因为投资者和用户通常更倾向于与真实、透明的团队合作，如果团队成员匿名，他们可能会认为项目没有足够的诚信和可信度，从而无法吸引足够的投资和用户。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">综上所述，匿名团队可能会对区块链项目的发展带来不利影响，因此，投资者和用户应该谨慎考虑是否参与匿名团队开发的项目。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">2.2 资金</span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">Radiant Capital项目成立至今没有 IDO、私募或风险投资的参与，早期项目所有的运营成本都是由团队成员自行筹集。</span>Radiant协议发展至今算是成功的完成了早期的冷启动，并吸引到了一定的用户基数，能为协议带来稳定收入（如下图2-1所示），从而cover一定的运营成本。但协议目前财库的具体情况未知。</p><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/2023071118422178995899.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"1\" data-index=\"1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"j-lazy\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/21/441455963652165.png?type=resource&amp;id=441455963652165&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://admin.1000mz.com/prod-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/21/441455963652165.png\" alt=\"研报｜跨链DeFi借贷协议Radiant Capital\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border-style: none; vertical-align: top; height: auto;\" /></a></figure><p><br/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">图2-1 Radiant Capital收益分成</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">此外，Radiant Capital作为Arbitrum上的一个全链借贷协议，在此前的Arbitrum DAOs Airdrop活动中，收到了 334 万枚 $ARB 代币，截至当下（2023年4月7日），价值近 400 万美元，是获空投的 DAO 中的第七大金额。</p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); margin: 32px 0px 16px; font-size: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--theme-line-color); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\">2.3代码</span></h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">据团队介绍，Radiant Capital的代码建立在2021年Fantom借贷协议Geist的基础上，而Geist又是使用Aave代码库建立的[5]。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Radiant Capital代码库暂未开源。不过据团队披露，Radiant v1已由PeckShield和Solidity Finance审核，而Radiant v2（主要由与Radiant v1相同的代码库组成）也与Peckshield和Zokyo进行了多次全面审计。同时，Radiant还聘请了BlockSec进行白帽攻击，以测试网络的安全性。这些审计的完整报告可通过Radiant官方文档查阅。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">目前Radiant Capital与Immunefi合作推出漏洞赏金计划，赏金最高达20万美元。此外Radiant将使用OpenZeppelin Defender的安全系统来全天候地监控网络，并对潜在的攻击/风险做出即使响应。</p><p><br/></p>', NULL, NULL, 'Y');
INSERT INTO `cms_article_detail` VALUES (441455394152517, 440515705974853, '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.8; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">《AIGC发展研究报告1.0》是清华大学元宇宙文化实验室倾力打造的成果。该报告融汇全球各国在AIGC领域的政策制定、企业战略部署及产业实践经验，汇聚了行业发展、学术研究与社会理念，致力于为广大读者普及AIGC知识体系，提供全面了解AIGC动态的指南。与此同时，《报告》涉猎当下AIGC研究的热点议题，该报告至少有60%的内容是由AIGC自动生成。《报告》共分为技术篇、产业篇、评测篇、职业篇、风险篇、哲理篇以及未来篇七个部分，旨在对AIGC发展趋势进行科学预测与展望，为读者提供有益的参考依据。</p><p><br/></p><figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; table-layout: fixed; color: rgb(38, 38, 38); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Ubuntu, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans CN&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: table !important;\"><a class=\"j-wpcom-lightbox\" href=\"http://www.liandu24.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/image-5-1024x576.png\" data-group=\"0\" data-id=\"0\" data-index=\"0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; background-color: initial; color: var(--theme-color);\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"iurl://resources/image/2023/07/21/441455920934981.png?type=resource&amp;id=441455920934981&amp;st=Local&amp;sid=440515705974853\" data-original=\"http://admin.1000mz.com/prod-api/preview/gzmdrw/resources/image/2023/07/21/441455920934981.png\" alt=\"报告｜清华大学《AIGC发展研究报告1.0》\" class=\"wp-image-35076 j-lazy\" width=\"820\"