 overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;\">二、报名方式及报名网址</strong></p></section></section></section><section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 10px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; background-color: rgb(235, 246, 255); visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 2px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; visibility: visible;\"><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.2667em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">考生登录教育部教育考试院公布的考生报名网站进行网上报名。报名网址入口（公网）：<strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;\">https://ncre-bm.neea.cn。</strong></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.2667em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">（一）考生报名要求</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.2667em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">1.报名者不受年龄、职业、学历等背景的限制，均可根据自己学习情况和实际能力选考相应的级别和科目。同次考试同一考生只能在一个省级承办机构的一个考点报名，最多可报三个科目，且不允许重复报考同一个科目。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.2667em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2.考生本人在规定时间内登录网站进行报名，按操作程序及要求输入报名信息和上传照片并申请审核。经审核通过后，直接在网上缴纳报名考试费。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.2667em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">3.考生必须认真填报信息自行确认，并按规定要求上传照片。如果填报信息有误，责任自负。考生上传照片即为准考证上的照片，若不符合规定或无法确认为考生本人的，考生将无法参加考试。</p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 2px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.2667em; visibility: visible; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">（二）照片信息标准</p></section></section></p><p><br/></p>', NULL, NULL, '0');
INSERT INTO `cms_article_detail` VALUES (641755664429125, 440515705974853, '<section style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-wrap-mode: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 2px; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.25em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; visibility: visible;\">近日，贵州省科学技术协会公布了《关于2025年度贵州省科协决策咨询调研课题及学术交流活动拟立项资助名单的公示》，我校杨晓老师申报的青年课题《智慧康养：贵州省康养产业科技赋能路径与策略研究》、杨尚钊老师申报的青年课题《返乡创（就）业青年对乡村社会公共服务设施需求研究》喜获立项。</span></p><p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2.25em; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; visibility: visible;\">此次2025年度贵州省科协决策咨询调研课题及学术交流活动我校共获批立项2项，立项数在贵州民办高校中位列第一，这也是我校首次获此课题立项，实现了该领域零的突破，特此向全校师生报喜！向获得立项的老师们表示祝贺!</span></p></section><p><br/></p><section style=\"-webk